    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AEROFLOT IL-62 (USSR) -This is USSR's largest and\nlatest passenger aircraft serving on Tokyo - Moscow - Paris.\nLondon etc and other main routes. Four turbo-fan engines\nare placed at the tail of the fuselage. thus minimizing the\nnoise in the passenger's cabin. Seating capacity: 70-186\nCruising speed 900kph. Maximum range\n9.000 km.\nPOST CARD\nAFFIX\nSTAMP\nHERE\n***\n§ PUB HEY NEC (NIPPON BEAUTY CARD CENTER) INCH\nNBC\nDOO-00\n015166.0086"
    ],
